release_info.name: Version 2.0.0
release_info.body:
Latest development version from main branch.

Latest commit: 7ef6d60
Date: 2025-10-28T18:27:40Z
Message: Add unit tests for ThemeManager and VersionManager

Introduces comprehensive unit tests for ThemeManager (theme loading, switching, color management, and callback registration) and VersionManager (version checking, caching, update logic, and version comparison). Also updates TODO.md to reflect completed testing and packaging milestones, and recent accomplishments for v2.0.0.
